      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Hard to fault RUNAWAY TYCOON (2) who is flying for the new yard including back-to-back dominant wins. Raced on speed and ran right away last time to score by six lengths. Looks hard to run down again. DAD BOD (7) placed here two back behind RUNAWAY TYCOON then was well off best last time in the race won by Auxiliary. Better drawn and down in weight so well worth another chance. BRUNO BRUNO (4) raced on speed and boxed on well to place here fresh. Fitter and is a speedy type who will take catching. BON'S YOUR BACK (3) is a former NSW galloper making his NT debut and does have a good fresh record. Worth watching. Same goes for RIVKIN (1) who is also a former NSW galloper with a strong fresh record. One to watch.",
